         <img alt="" class="thumbimage" data-file-height="816" data-file-width="1224" decoding="async" height="147" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/2562670_Arnold_Schwarzenegger_in_Kuwait_2016.jpg/220px-2562670_Arnold_Schwarzenegger_in_Kuwait_2016.jpg" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/2562670_Arnold_Schwarzenegger_in_Kuwait_2016.jpg/330px-2562670_Arnold_Schwarzenegger_in_Kuwait_2016.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/2562670_Arnold_Schwarzenegger_in_Kuwait_2016.jpg/440px-2562670_Arnold_Schwarzenegger_in_Kuwait_2016.jpg 2x" width="220"/>
